Big Brother Naija 2018 housemate, Angel Awotarigha has found his missing rib. The reality TV star tied the knot with his Canadian girlfriend, Felicia, on Tuesday, April 30th in Port Harcourt. Sharing a photo of the both of them rocking the Ijaw traditional outfit, Angel wrote: “See Ijaw people, thank you all for your love and support, I give you Mr and Mrs Angel Awotarigha”. Congrats, Angel! See the photo below: Former big brother naija housemate, Angel and his bride. | Photo: Angel/Instagram